      "role": "user",
      "content": "yeah i see the null pointer thing, i'll check the lookup logic. but what's weird is that it's not happening every single time. most of the time the coupon loads fine, but then it'll just randomly fail on a valid code. it's super inconsistent. why would it be null sometimes but not others if the code is the same?",
